<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٨٤٢ - وَعَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4427">عُقْبَةَ بْنِ صُهْبَانَ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3935">عَبْدَ اللهِ بْنَ الْمُغَفَّلِ المُزَنِيِّ </a>: <span class="c2">«فِي الْبَوْلِ فِي الْمُغْتَسَلِ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>